msg: - java.util.jar.Attributes has one unpleasent drawback: It is backed by a HashMap, so insertion order of entries is not retained and Implemention-URL lands in the middle of nowhere.
- Note to m-(javadoc|jar|etc.)-plugin implementors: if your are using 2.6 and plexus archiver, you *must* upgrade plexus archiver to 2.2 otherwise your plugin won't compile due to a missing symbol
